text: Holowaty (may be spelled as Holovaty, Holovatyi) is a Ukrainian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Bill Holowaty, American baseball coach. *Daniel Holowaty (born 1989), American soccer player. *Paul Holowaty (born 1985), English actor *Serhiy Holovatyi, Ukrainian politician. ==See also== *Holovatsky Category:Ukrainian-language surnames
title: Holowaty
